      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered this car since day one, and it's been garage-kept and meticulously loved. If you're looking for something that's practically perfect and ready for your next big adventure, this is definitely the one. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how pristine it is. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
