      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather remains supple with no visible bolster wear, and every switch and electronic feature operates with factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records documenting preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. From the spotless undercarriage to the flawless alloy wheels, this is an uncompromising example for the most discerning enthusiast. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
