      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that's basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
